Class InRoomFilter

java.lang.Object
hac.filters.InRoomFilter
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.springframework.web.servlet.HandlerInterceptor
public class InRoomFilter extends Object implements org.springframework.web.servlet.HandlerInterceptor
The filter makes sure that if a player (which means a user inside a room) enters pages that aren't in game related, he will be removed from its room.
